## Prerequisites Confirmation

### nipyapi Profile

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| **Profile Name** | `{{ nipyapi_profile }}` |

### Verify Installation

Run the following to confirm nipyapi is installed and the profile is reachable:

```bash
# Check nipyapi version (must be >= 1.2.0)
nipyapi --version

# Verify profile exists
grep "{{ nipyapi_profile }}:" ~/.nipyapi/profiles.yml

# Test connectivity to your runtime
nipyapi --profile {{ nipyapi_profile }} canvas get_root_pg_id
```

If connectivity fails with a 401 error, regenerate your Personal Access Token from the Snowflake UI and update the `nifi_bearer_token` in `~/.nipyapi/profiles.yml`.
